edu.uic.cs.dmtm.apriori

Class Item

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.uic.cs.dmtm.apriori.Item
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<Item>

    public class Item
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Item>
    A representation of an Item. The item is represented as a String and carries information about its minimum support, actual support and support count. Implements the Comparable interface to provide an ordering capability to the items; items order is lexicographical on the id.
    Author:
    Marco Mele, Massimo Piras
